video.title: Quantico
video.synopsis: When evidence in a deadly terrorist attack implicates FBI trainee Alex Parrish, she must discover which one of her classmates framed her.

episodes.synopsis: FBI recruit Alex Parrish hides a secret past while training to be an agent. Nine months later, the bureau suspects her in a major terrorist attack.
episodes.title: Run

episodes.synopsis: The trainees are assigned to unearth threats to national security. On the run, Alex must outsmart Liam and his team to access her apartment.
episodes.title: America

episodes.synopsis: Alex receives information about her father's FBI past while the trainees learn the art of profiling. Alex's mother begs Alex to turn herself in.
episodes.title: Cover

episodes.synopsis: Alex doubts her abilities after a hostage rescue exercise leaves her shaken. A clue leads Alex to question the innocence of a fellow FBI classmate.
episodes.title: Kill

episodes.synopsis: The trainees leave campus for the first time to work on an undercover assignment. Alex decides to tell her side of the story in a public interview.
episodes.title: Found

episodes.synopsis: The trainees learn surveillance techniques by applying them to Miranda and her son Charlie. Alex receives some help hacking into an FBI computer.
episodes.title: God

episodes.synopsis: Not every trainee advances past the midterm exams. Trying to clear her name, Alex finds Nimah and Raina, who provide more questions than answers.
episodes.title: Go

episodes.synopsis: The trainees realize that their individual assignments are connected. Confidential FBI files are leaked, leading Alex to believe there's another bomb.
episodes.title: Over

episodes.synopsis: A guest speaker assigns the trainees to examine serial killer cases, but Simon uncovers something disturbing. Alex is interrogated by an expert team.
episodes.title: Guilty

episodes.synopsis: Truths are uncovered when the trainees are assigned to review and select near year's class. Alex works in secret with allies to find the bomber.
episodes.title: Quantico

episodes.synopsis: A holiday break isn't a cause for celebration for some recruits. The terrorists behind the Grand Central Station bombing are finally revealed.
episodes.title: Inside

episodes.synopsis: A new group of trainees joins Alex and her class, causing friction and competition. Alex testifies before Congress about the terrorist bombings.
episodes.title: Alex

episodes.synopsis: The trainees are tasked to develop confidential informants in the real world. Alex and a fellow agent are forced to reveal classified intel.
episodes.title: Clear

episodes.synopsis: The trainees learn defensive driving techniques. Alex visits Simon in Vermont, where he is struggling to cope with his difficult new reality.
episodes.title: Answer

episodes.synopsis: Shelby learns some shocking news. When terrorists attack the agents, Miranda pays a heavy price. Alex gets a new mission from the terrorist.
episodes.title: Turn

episodes.synopsis: While a review board analyzes the terrorist attack, an airplane hijacking exercise proves to be overwhelming for Shelby. Alex finds a surprising ally.
episodes.title: Clue

episodes.synopsis: Liam and Miranda assign the trainees to cross an international border without identification. Simon risks his life to help Alex find the terrorist.
episodes.title: Care

episodes.synopsis: The trainees uncover surprising truths about each other in a background check exercise. Alex contacts Claire Haas and learns what happened to Caleb.
episodes.title: Soon

episodes.synopsis: The trainees meet with various FBI branches to select career paths. Alex's terrorist hunt leads her to a familiar face who knows her target's plans.
episodes.title: Fast

episodes.synopsis: Weeks before graduation, Alex and Ryan work a case at a field office. Alex's trust is shaken when she learns new information about someone she loves.
episodes.title: Drive

episodes.synopsis: The trainees prepare to graduate and leave Quantico for their first assignments. Alex discovers that she's at the heart of another terrorist attack.
episodes.title: Right

episodes.synopsis: As graduation day arrives, not every trainee is in a celebratory mood. Alex and her team discover the true identity of the terrorist mastermind.
episodes.title: Yes

episodes.synopsis: Now working for the CIA, Alex Parrish finds herself enmeshed in a sinister conspiracy that involves foes from her past.
episodes.title: KUDOVE

episodes.synopsis: While taking stock of their relationship, Alex and Ryan undergo counterintelligence training. In the present timeline, Raina tries to ID a terrorist.
episodes.title: LIPSTICK

episodes.synopsis: In flashbacks, the new CIA recruits focus on assessment training. Meanwhile, in the present, Alex attempts to infiltrate a terrorist group.
episodes.title: STESCALADE

episodes.synopsis: The trainees undergo drills designed to test their ability to endure stress. In the present timeline, the terrorists demand an exchange of prisoners.
episodes.title: KUBARK

episodes.synopsis: Harry digs deeper into Alex and Ryan's past, and Owen recruits Leon for a special project. In the present, Alex finds herself in a tough spot.
episodes.title: KMFORGET

episodes.synopsis: Memories come flooding back when Alex learns that her next assignment involves a drone strike. In the present timeline, Alex has doubts about Lydia.
episodes.title: AQUILINE

episodes.synopsis: Owen gives the trainees an unusual lesson on enhanced interrogation techniques. In the present, a new president takes office.
episodes.title: LCFLUTTER

episodes.synopsis: As Thanksgiving nears, the recruits learn the importance of eliminating personal relationships. In the present, Alex attempts to disarm the weapon.
episodes.title: ODENVY

episodes.synopsis: The recruits are schooled in seduction and Alex puts her training to use with Owen. In the present timeline, Alex's persistence finally pays off.
episodes.title: CLEOPATRA

episodes.synopsis: Owen and the recruits brainstorm how to turn a high-ranking Venezuelan official. In the present, the president implements a plan to end the crisis.
episodes.title: JMPALM

episodes.synopsis: While Alex explains her traitor theory to Owen, the recruits deal with a difficult target. In the present timeline, the terrorists try a new tactic.
episodes.title: ZRTORCH

episodes.synopsis: Eager to protect their privacy, the recruits break into the NSA to delete their personal information. In the present, the hostages form a plan.
episodes.title: FALLENORACLE

episodes.synopsis: The FBI visits the Farm following a mysterious death. Meanwhile, in the present timeline, Alex returns to the crisis zone with a mission.
episodes.title: EPICSHELTER

episodes.synopsis: President Haas assembles a joint task force consisting of CIA and FBI agents to operate outside the law and expose a global conspiracy.
episodes.title: LNWILT

episodes.synopsis: After giving Clay the lowdown on Alex, Ryan and the others, Owen leads an investigation into an explosion that isn't what it seems.
episodes.title: MOCKINGBIRD

episodes.synopsis: The team investigates a power broker who supposedly accessed stolen surveillance. Alex forms a connection with an asset.
episodes.title: MKTOPAZ

episodes.synopsis: Alex steps up to help a friend who was framed for a serious crime. Meanwhile, the political landscape pushes the task force into new territory.
episodes.title: ODYOKE

episodes.synopsis: Clay gets an unexpected visitor. Alex pushes back to save the president's reputation. Owen receives some tough love.
episodes.title: KUMONK

episodes.synopsis: The task force's mission: get all the collaborators into one place and get them to betray each other. But no mission goes exactly as planned.
episodes.title: MHORDER

episodes.synopsis: While working undercover to infiltrate the collaborators, Alex begins to doubt the worthiness of her mission and her role in it.
episodes.title: GLOBALREACH

episodes.synopsis: Owen fears the collaborators are nearing the final stages of their plan. The task force races to stop a sinister threat that could change everything.
episodes.title: RAINBOW

episodes.synopsis: As the team tries to secretly thwart Roarke's ambitions, the possibility of a new Constitutional amendment looms over the country.
episodes.title: RESISTANCE

episodes.synopsis: Alex is forced to abandon her peaceful existence in Italy when she gets word that Shelby has been kidnapped by a sinister arms dealer.
episodes.title: The Conscience Code

episodes.synopsis: In an effort to uncover those responsible for a viral outbreak, Ryan goes undercover in a white supremacist group.
episodes.title: Fear and Flesh

episodes.synopsis: With a brutal drug kingpin's trial on the horizon, the team is tasked with protecting the star witness, a troubled ex-CIA agent.
episodes.title: Hell's Gate

episodes.synopsis: After Harry receives a tip about a possible assassination on American soil, Owen orders the team to be on high alert during a glitzy gala.
episodes.title: Spy Games

episodes.synopsis: A physics professor steals 10 pounds of uranium, setting off an intense search ahead of an international summit in New York.
episodes.title: The Blood of Romeo

episodes.synopsis: Jocelyn reflects on the mission that changed her life and finds herself in a position to exact revenge.
episodes.title: The Heavens Fall

episodes.synopsis: Still reeling from a shocking loss, the team is assigned to protect a scientist whose work could inflict massive damage.
episodes.title: Bullet Train

episodes.synopsis: With a personal problem lingering in the back of her mind, Alex goes undercover with a military contractor suspected of being a traitor.
episodes.title: Deep Cover

episodes.synopsis: Following an attempt on Shelby's life, the team questions whether a face from her past is really worth protecting.
episodes.title: Fear Feargach

episodes.synopsis: Faced with the disturbing reality that their families are fair game, Alex and company set out to track a killer before it's too late.
episodes.title: No Place Is Home

episodes.synopsis: As Devlin's fiendish plan takes shape, the team searches a book for clues to his next move. Meanwhile, Owen and Jocelyn clear the air.
episodes.title: The Art Of War

episodes.synopsis: As Harry's patience regarding his sister's whereabouts wears thin, Alex and her team accompany Devlin on a flight to Ireland.
episodes.title: Ghosts

episodes.synopsis: Finding herself in hostile territory, Alex discovers -- much to her horror -- that she may have underestimated her enemy.
episodes.title: Who Are You?
